{"tid":1917387,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[支持Rthk] 台灣故事：會客菜","createTime":"2020-03-09T12:53:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-09T15:13:06.000Z","uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1dabea03064f3442f56e3618ba7ddb7220df7af0","tid":1917387,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T12:53:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/mCLp0pjof0A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FmCLp0pjof0A&d=80SwoNSEtZKcYq6iNhm%2FM4nGVh3W70%2FpCcVRRx8QUyg%3D&h=59b20e00\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/mCLp0pjof0A</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n在台灣大大小小的監獄附近，都總會找到一兩間不甚起眼的食檔；既無大魚大肉，亦不是甚麼撚手菜色，普普通通的小菜，賣的是家常味道，監獄裡面稱之為會客菜。會客菜給囚犯重拾少少家的滋味，在不經意間救贖了獄中痛悔心靈，熱騰騰的香味將罪人渡向新生。<br />\n<br />\n#一碗滷肉飯令人改過自新,#江湖大佬都幫襯的食檔,#監獄食物禁忌,#香腸雞鴨不可一齊點,#人生有take two"},{"pid":"8a4fecfcfacbb0954fabf3b2798f1a3b1834565b","tid":1917387,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-09T15:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}